{"tid":1481691,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[8.18維園見呀] 街坊力量都仲係爭少少 爭一樣嘢","createTime":"2019-08-17T20:15:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T03:18:30.000Z","uid":40170,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9e0c1b3f0ce81c75186b5451b93f75107307154a","tid":1481691,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T20:15:19.000Z","msg":"對狗叫「黑社會」當然係需要啦<br />\n加埋對手足講「抗爭有理」<br />\n<del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">甚至係「香港抗爭者好嘢 支持抗爭者嚴正抗爭」</span></del><br />\n之類嘅口號就完美啦<br />\n<br />\n咁多日嚟最深刻嘅撚狗圖都係嗰張九宮格<br />\n外面八格多謝公務員 <br />\n中間嗰格係喺狗徽上面寫「唔係你」<br />\n<br />\n邊緣化佢地就啱<br />\n一定要有記者record到把聲<br />\n<br />\n全面否定垃圾軍政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n匡正我城 推倒重來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同唔同意都好<br />\n一陣見。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ec73aa6460a7bc3a09c3cd4c823b236dfd7bd7","tid":1481691,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T20:16:25.000Z","msg":"Pish 聽日見<br />\n拎齊gear 用唔用就到時決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee24b5adce4b7f1f2fdb2bbadf182a192337dbcd","tid":1481691,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T20:18:25.000Z","msg":"無比較 無傷害<br />\n有比較 很傷害<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde411398096e72b8fb93d32deef80d4b05e39eb","tid":1481691,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T20:20:56.000Z","msg":"細細力pish一嘢<br />\n街坊都一齊進化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgm